<cb:div type="cbeta-notes">
<head>CBETA 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0573b12" resp="#resp3" type="mod_biao" target="#nkr_note_mod_biao_0573b12">說經將訖舍利弗<choice cb:resp="#resp2"><corr>已</corr><sic>巳</sic></choice>慶美于上帝釋復欣其所遇而致歎也此經言簡義該大乘微妙之旨神通感應之力一時備領所以歎未曾有也</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div type="xuzang-notes">
<head>卍續藏 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0573b12" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0573b12">說經將訖舍利弗巳慶美于上帝釋復欣其所遇而致歎也此經言簡義該大乘微妙之旨神通感應之力一時備領所以歎未曾有也</note>
<note n="0574b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0574b01">三世菩提妙道具載此經若受持護養即供養三世諸佛故助汝喜</note>
<note n="0574b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0574b02">以上財供校受持受持即法供養也如未將成法供養義故引成事以為證</note>
<note n="0574b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0574b03">若財供養則於佛無用於眾生無益故非所欣也如來積劫累功本為眾生若奉順經典如說修行則稱悅聖心乃真供養也</note>
<note n="0574b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0574b04">深經者取藏經中深義說實相等也此下盡是廣歎深經未明法供養義也</note>
<note n="0574b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0574b05">藏以法藏印以總持豈常人能闚<g ref="#CB00438">𨵦</g>乎</note>
<note n="0574b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0574b06">深經所說非有非無順因緣法也法從緣生則無自性為主即無我人壽命即空無相無作無起此深經所順也</note>
<note n="0574b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0574b07">依實相辯四非常乃曰明也</note>
<note n="0574b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0574b08">十二因緣以下明得無生忍心以實智慧隨順實法也</note>
<note n="0574b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0574b09">至義非言宣尋言則失故不依語</note>
<note n="0574b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0574b10">滅生于不滅畢竟滅則無不滅滅無所滅故曰無盡相</note>
<note n="0574b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0574b11">此即四依中如實法也</note>
<note n="0574b12" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0574b12">月蓋道力未具恐為魔所壞故請加威神</note>
<note n="0575b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0575b01">陀羅尼是聞持也</note>
</p>
